    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆《睡美人》的全新诠释  </strong></h2>不知何时醒来的睡公主以及世界命运的走向。<br>这是一部以著名的童话故事《荆棘公主》为基础，并对其进行全新诠释的视觉小说。<br>挥洒着如同恶魔般的想象力和创造力的游戏创作者们，将带领玩家走进一个幻想世界。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/1e4f2997be8141849ab6ce089a802a67.poster.avif?t=1709769157\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/1e4f2997be8141849ab6ce089a802a67.webm?t=1709769157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/1e4f2997be8141849ab6ce089a802a67.mp4?t=1709769157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/bc120fefc8ca27bd0a7d8f4b0c9a536c.poster.avif?t=1709769157\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/bc120fefc8ca27bd0a7d8f4b0c9a536c.webm?t=1709769157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/bc120fefc8ca27bd0a7d8f4b0c9a536c.mp4?t=1709769157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆传说的游戏创作者和当下最具人气的艺术家合作</strong></h2>曾参与制作《女神转生》以及《真·女神转生》的传奇人物<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/suzuki.PNG?t=1709769157\" /></span><br>剧本：铃木一也<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/masuko.PNG?t=1709769157\" /></span><br>音乐：增子津可灿<br><br>举世瞩目的幻想画师，艺术之战的世界冠军。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/aogachou.PNG?t=1709769157\" /></span><br>人物设计/美术：Aogachou<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【剧情简介】</strong></h2>公主是一位深受神明喜爱的少女。在其出生后赐予其这个世上最美好的恩惠（天赋），其中包括：美丽、高雅、柔和、宽容、诚实、忍耐……<br>直到公主十六岁生日前，她都在国王和王后的宠爱下过着这个世界上最幸福的生活。然而，在全国举办庆祝和祭祀的当天，那个附着于公主身上的诅咒得到了应验。第十三位魔女闰月对公主施加了一个可怕的诅咒……那就是公主会被纺锤刺伤，并陷入永恒的沉睡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/be45a57d6b30f949f54a2b15f4ca1bcc.poster.avif?t=1709769157\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/be45a57d6b30f949f54a2b15f4ca1bcc.webm?t=1709769157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/be45a57d6b30f949f54a2b15f4ca1bcc.mp4?t=1709769157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>然而公主并没有就此死亡。躺在天篷床下的她掉进了一个深不见底的梦中世界。被荆棘缠绕的城堡与世界隔绝，而魔女在床垫边上独自一人默默地守在公主身边。从那之后一直形影不离……过着仅有两人的生活。而在百年之后，勇敢的王子冲破了重重荆棘围困，来到了公主的身旁。王子对沉睡中的公主一见钟情，并轻轻地吻了她……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/84607965c95364e83782d320342099d6.poster.avif?t=1709769157\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/84607965c95364e83782d320342099d6.webm?t=1709769157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/84607965c95364e83782d320342099d6.mp4?t=1709769157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>童话故事到此公主醒来从此过着幸福的生活。然而……在这里公主并没有如期醒来。未能接受王子爱意的公主继续陷入沉睡之中……闰月在旁冷静地注视着这一切。<br>自那之后具体过了多少年呢……正值百年之际，一位新的“王子”来到了公主身旁。到底他是历史人物，还是名流千古的传说之人……或是来自异界的使者呢？<br>最终能够将真爱之情传达给陷入梦中的公主，并唤醒她的人到底是谁呢……？？然后寄托于公主的秘密、以及魔女的真正目的又是？这些谜团仍然等待被揭晓。请大家打开魔法之门，悄悄地窥探一下公主的卧室，并找出其中的答案吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆角色配音</h2>荆棘公主：<strong>森田凉花</strong>　<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/princess.PNG?t=1709769157\" /></span><br><br>魔女闰月：<strong>ςera➹</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/witch_uru.PNG?t=1709769157\" /></span><br><br>使魔格里马金：<strong>大冢明夫</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/furimalkin.PNG?t=1709769157\" /></span><br><br>黑王子：<strong>置鲇龙太郎</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/black_prince.PNG?t=1709769157\" /></span><br><br>女王：<strong>冈村明美</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/queen.PNG?t=1709769157\" /></span><br><br>尸形公主：<strong>加隈亚衣</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798750/extras/corpse_princess.PNG?t=1709769157\" /></span>",
